\par 
\par (Acts 22:16)  And now why tarriest thou? arise, and be baptized, and wash away thy sins, calling on the name of the Lord.
\par 
\par (Rom 6:3-4)  Know ye not, that so many of us as were baptized into Jesus Christ were baptized into his death? \{4\}
